{"type":"message","id":"bd52eb97","parentId":"77e5f1ec","timestamp":"2026-03-03T07:03:03.003Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"QVeris工具有问题，参数没有正确传递。让我尝试用不同的方式来执行。也许我应该直接使用curl访问Finnhub API，但需要一个API key。\n\n让我检查一下是否有其他工具可以用，或者我可以使用QVeris的聚合工具来获取新闻。","thinkingSignature":"64f9d1d759d0bc482b92f3b4c80bca622eef7f52a68ed10ea12641e47e4c9c0e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_p2rixd95nzkp_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace && node scripts/qveris_tool.mjs search \"finance news aggregation with relevance score\" --limit 5","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":16796,"output":121,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30901,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772521378070}}
{"type":"message","id":"4efb28d9","parentId":"bd52eb97","timestamp":"2026-03-03T07:03:08.985Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_p2rixd95nzkp_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"finance news aggregation with relevance score\",\n  \"total\": 5,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"qveris_finance.finance_news_aggregation_v1\",\n      \"name\": \"Finance News Aggregation\",\n      \"description\": \"Search and aggregate financial news from multiple sources\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"query\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Search query for financial news\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Maximum number of results to return\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"Provider for finance-related skills\",\n      \"skill_type\": \"aggregation\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"eodhd.news.retrieve.v1.fe8bf94c\",\n      \"name\": \"Retrieve Financial News\",\n      \"description\": \"Returns the latest financial news headlines and full articles for a given ticker symbol or topic tag. Requires either a ticker (s) or a tag (t). Supports filtering by date, pagination, and JSON response format.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"s\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The ticker code to retrieve news for, for example: AAPL.US\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"t\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The topic tag to retrieve news for, for example: technology\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Start date for filtering news (YYYY-MM-DD)\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"End date for filtering news (YYYY-MM-DD)\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Number of results to return (default: 50, minimum: 1, maximum: 1000)\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"offset\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Offset for pagination (default: 0)\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"fmt\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Response format, either json or xml (default: json)\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {}\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Access historical end-of-day stock prices, intraday data, US stock options, and real-time prices with free and advanced plans. EODHD provides financial data for 150,000+ tickers, including stocks, ETFs, funds, and currencies worldwide.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1.183,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.741\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"alphavantage.news_sentiment.retrieve.v1.7aca3c4a\",\n      \"name\": \"Retrieve Market News & Sentiment\",\n      \"description\": \"Returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from premier news outlets around the world, covering stocks, cryptocurrencies, forex, and various financial topics.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"function\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The function name.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"tickers\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of stock/crypto/forex symbols (e.g., COIN,CRYPTO:BTC,FOREX:USD). Filters articles that mention all listed tickers.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"topics\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of topics. Articles must cover all listed topics.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"blockchain\",\n            \"earnings\",\n            \"ipo\",\n            \"mergers_and_acquisitions\",\n            \"financial_markets\",\n            \"economy_fiscal\",\n            \"economy_monetary\",\n            \"economy_macro\",\n            \"energy_transportation\",\n            \"finance\",\n            \"life_sciences\",\n            \"manufacturing\",\n            \"real_estate\",\n            \"retail_wholesale\",\n            \"technology\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Start time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format (e.g., 20220410T0130).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"End time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sort\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Sorting method.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"LATEST\",\n            \"EARLIEST\",\n            \"RELEVANCE\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Maximum number of results (up to 1000).\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"function\": \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 660.49,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.973\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"alphavantage.news_sentiment.query.v1.7aca3c4a\",\n      \"name\": \"Market News & Sentiment\",\n      \"description\": \"Returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from global news outlets covering stocks, crypto, forex, and economic topics.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"function\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The function to call. In this case, NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"tickers\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of stock/crypto/forex symbols to filter articles by (e.g., AAPL,CRYPTO:BTC).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"topics\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of topics to filter by.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"blockchain\",\n            \"earnings\",\n            \"ipo\",\n            \"mergers_and_acquisitions\",\n            \"financial_markets\",\n            \"economy_fiscal\",\n            \"economy_monetary\",\n            \"economy_macro\",\n            \"energy_transportation\",\n            \"finance\",\n            \"life_sciences\",\n            \"manufacturing\",\n            \"real_estate\",\n            \"retail_wholesale\",\n            \"technology\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Start time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format (e.g., 20220410T0130).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"End time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sort\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Sorting method for results.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"LATEST\",\n            \"EARLIEST\",\n            \"RELEVANCE\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Maximum number of results (up to 1000).\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"function\": \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 520.43,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.987\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"finnhub.news.retrieve.v1.2e72ea5d\",\n      \"name\": \"Market News\",\n      \"description\": \"Get latest market news.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"category\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"This parameter can be 1 of the following values <code>general, forex, crypto, merger</code>.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"minId\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Use this field to get only news after this ID. Default to 0\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"category\": \"general\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Finnhub - Free APIs for realtime stock, forex, and cryptocurrency. Company fundamentals, Economic data, and Alternative data.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"search_id\": \"406d7dda-35de-4e5e-9c2c-99e1dc63b71c\",\n  \"elapsed_time_ms\": 312.29\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":5978,"aggregated":"{\n  \"query\": \"finance news aggregation with relevance score\",\n  \"total\": 5,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"qveris_finance.finance_news_aggregation_v1\",\n      \"name\": \"Finance News Aggregation\",\n      \"description\": \"Search and aggregate financial news from multiple sources\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"query\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Search query for financial news\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Maximum number of results to return\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"Provider for finance-related skills\",\n      \"skill_type\": \"aggregation\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"eodhd.news.retrieve.v1.fe8bf94c\",\n      \"name\": \"Retrieve Financial News\",\n      \"description\": \"Returns the latest financial news headlines and full articles for a given ticker symbol or topic tag. Requires either a ticker (s) or a tag (t). Supports filtering by date, pagination, and JSON response format.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"s\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The ticker code to retrieve news for, for example: AAPL.US\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"t\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The topic tag to retrieve news for, for example: technology\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Start date for filtering news (YYYY-MM-DD)\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"End date for filtering news (YYYY-MM-DD)\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Number of results to return (default: 50, minimum: 1, maximum: 1000)\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"offset\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Offset for pagination (default: 0)\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"fmt\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Response format, either json or xml (default: json)\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {}\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Access historical end-of-day stock prices, intraday data, US stock options, and real-time prices with free and advanced plans. EODHD provides financial data for 150,000+ tickers, including stocks, ETFs, funds, and currencies worldwide.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1.183,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.741\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"alphavantage.news_sentiment.retrieve.v1.7aca3c4a\",\n      \"name\": \"Retrieve Market News & Sentiment\",\n      \"description\": \"Returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from premier news outlets around the world, covering stocks, cryptocurrencies, forex, and various financial topics.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"function\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The function name.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"tickers\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of stock/crypto/forex symbols (e.g., COIN,CRYPTO:BTC,FOREX:USD). Filters articles that mention all listed tickers.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"topics\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of topics. Articles must cover all listed topics.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"blockchain\",\n            \"earnings\",\n            \"ipo\",\n            \"mergers_and_acquisitions\",\n            \"financial_markets\",\n            \"economy_fiscal\",\n            \"economy_monetary\",\n            \"economy_macro\",\n            \"energy_transportation\",\n            \"finance\",\n            \"life_sciences\",\n            \"manufacturing\",\n            \"real_estate\",\n            \"retail_wholesale\",\n            \"technology\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Start time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format (e.g., 20220410T0130).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"End time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sort\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Sorting method.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"LATEST\",\n            \"EARLIEST\",\n            \"RELEVANCE\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Maximum number of results (up to 1000).\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"function\": \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 660.49,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.973\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"alphavantage.news_sentiment.query.v1.7aca3c4a\",\n      \"name\": \"Market News & Sentiment\",\n      \"description\": \"Returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from global news outlets covering stocks, crypto, forex, and economic topics.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"function\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The function to call. In this case, NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"tickers\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of stock/crypto/forex symbols to filter articles by (e.g., AAPL,CRYPTO:BTC).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"topics\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of topics to filter by.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"blockchain\",\n            \"earnings\",\n            \"ipo\",\n            \"mergers_and_acquisitions\",\n            \"financial_markets\",\n            \"economy_fiscal\",\n            \"economy_monetary\",\n            \"economy_macro\",\n            \"energy_transportation\",\n            \"finance\",\n            \"life_sciences\",\n            \"manufacturing\",\n            \"real_estate\",\n            \"retail_wholesale\",\n            \"technology\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Start time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format (e.g., 20220410T0130).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"End time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sort\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Sorting method for results.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"LATEST\",\n            \"EARLIEST\",\n            \"RELEVANCE\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Maximum number of results (up to 1000).\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"function\": \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs