{"type":"message","id":"90588258","parentId":"3d9c0c97","timestamp":"2026-03-03T07:04:35.848Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"QVeris似乎没有正确将参数传递给底层工具。这是一个配置问题。让我检查一下是否有其他方法可以获取Finnhub数据，或者看看QVeris是否有其他可用的工具。\n\n实际上，QVeris有一个\"查询\"函数 (query endpoint)，让我看看是否可以使用它来执行工具。或者，也许我应该报告给用户说QVeris的Finnhub工具有配置问题。\n\n让我先尝试看看QVeris是否有其他工具可以提供带有热度分数的财经新闻。","thinkingSignature":"f5dade692bd1f64d781ec92597ab0c577168a198c7a18e079249c017eee55fae"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_iwtm5dkzr7bx_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace && node scripts/qveris_tool.mjs search \"news sentiment relevance score\" --limit 10","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":21479,"output":163,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35626,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772521464278}}
{"type":"message","id":"9685bf10","parentId":"90588258","timestamp":"2026-03-03T07:04:41.050Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_iwtm5dkzr7bx_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"news sentiment relevance score\",\n  \"total\": 10,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"eodhd.sentiments.retrieve.v1.c2c27d35\",\n      \"name\": \"Retrieve Sentiment Data\",\n      \"description\": \"Get sentiment scores for one or more financial instruments (stocks, ETFs, crypto) calculated from news and social media, normalized on a scale from -1 (very negative) to 1 (very positive).\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"s\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"One or more comma-separated tickers, for example: AAPL.US,BTC-USD.CC\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Start date for filtering sentiment data (YYYY-MM-DD)\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"End date for filtering sentiment data (YYYY-MM-DD)\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"s\": \"AAPL.US,BTC-USD.CC\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Access historical end-of-day stock prices, intraday data, US stock options, and real-time prices with free and advanced plans. EODHD provides financial data for 150,000+ tickers, including stocks, ETFs, funds, and currencies worldwide.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1278.53,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.999\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"alphavantage.news_sentiment.query.v1.7aca3c4a\",\n      \"name\": \"Market News & Sentiment\",\n      \"description\": \"Returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from global news outlets covering stocks, crypto, forex, and economic topics.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"function\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The function to call. In this case, NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"tickers\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of stock/crypto/forex symbols to filter articles by (e.g., AAPL,CRYPTO:BTC).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"topics\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of topics to filter by.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"blockchain\",\n            \"earnings\",\n            \"ipo\",\n            \"mergers_and_acquisitions\",\n            \"financial_markets\",\n            \"economy_fiscal\",\n            \"economy_monetary\",\n            \"economy_macro\",\n            \"energy_transportation\",\n            \"finance\",\n            \"life_sciences\",\n            \"manufacturing\",\n            \"real_estate\",\n            \"retail_wholesale\",\n            \"technology\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Start time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format (e.g., 20220410T0130).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"End time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sort\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Sorting method for results.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"LATEST\",\n            \"EARLIEST\",\n            \"RELEVANCE\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Maximum number of results (up to 1000).\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"function\": \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 520.43,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.987\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"gdelt-data.doc.tonechart.retrieve.v2.a7b24341\",\n      \"name\": \"Retrieve Tone Chart\",\n      \"description\": \"Generates a histogram showing the distribution of article tones (from extremely negative to extremely positive) for articles mentioning a specific query over the last 3 months.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"query\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Search query phrase\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"mode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"API operation mode\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"tonechart\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"mode\": \"tonechart\",\n          \"query\": \"climate change\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"The Global Database of Events, Language, and Tone (GDELT) monitors the world's broadcast, print, and web news from nearly every corner of every country in over 100 languages and identifies the people, locations, organizations, counts, themes, sources, emotions, quotes, images and events driving our global society every second of every day. GDELT 2.0 updates every 15 minutes with new features including realtime translation of 65 languages and measurement of over 2,300 emotions and themes.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 19242.44,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.077\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"alphavantage.news_sentiment.retrieve.v1.7aca3c4a\",\n      \"name\": \"Retrieve Market News & Sentiment\",\n      \"description\": \"Returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from premier news outlets around the world, covering stocks, cryptocurrencies, forex, and various financial topics.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"function\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The function name.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"tickers\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of stock/crypto/forex symbols (e.g., COIN,CRYPTO:BTC,FOREX:USD). Filters articles that mention all listed tickers.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"topics\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of topics. Articles must cover all listed topics.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"blockchain\",\n            \"earnings\",\n            \"ipo\",\n            \"mergers_and_acquisitions\",\n            \"financial_markets\",\n            \"economy_fiscal\",\n            \"economy_monetary\",\n            \"economy_macro\",\n            \"energy_transportation\",\n            \"finance\",\n            \"life_sciences\",\n            \"manufacturing\",\n            \"real_estate\",\n            \"retail_wholesale\",\n            \"technology\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Start time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format (e.g., 20220410T0130).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"End time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sort\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Sorting method.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"LATEST\",\n            \"EARLIEST\",\n            \"RELEVANCE\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Maximum number of results (up to 1000).\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"function\": \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 660.49,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.973\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"alphavantage.news_sentiment.query.v1.467a92c0\",\n      \"name\": \"Market News & Sentiment Trending\",\n      \"description\": \"This API returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from a large & growing selection of premier news outlets around the world, covering stocks, cryptocurrencies, forex, and a wide range of topics such as fiscal policy, mergers & acquisitions, IPOs, etc.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"function\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The function of your choice. In this case, function=NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"tickers\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The stock/crypto/forex symbols of your choice. For example: tickers=IBM will filter for articles that mention the IBM ticker; tickers=COIN,CRYPTO:BTC,FOREX:USD will filter for articles that simultaneously mention Coinbase (COIN), Bitcoin (CRYPTO:BTC), and US Dollar (FOREX:USD) in their content.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"topics\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The news topics of your choice. For example: topics=technology will filter for articles that write about the technology sector; topics=technology,ipo will filter for articles that simultaneously cover technology and IPO in their content. Below is the full list of supported topics: Blockchain: blockchain, Earnings: earnings, IPO: ipo, Mergers & Acquisitions: mergers_and_acquisitions, Financial Markets: financial_markets, Economy - Fiscal Policy (e.g., tax reform, government spending): economy_fiscal, Economy - Monetary Policy (e.g., interest rates, inflation): economy_monetary, Economy - Macro/Overall: economy_macro, Energy & Transportation: energy_transportation, Finance: finance, Life Sciences: life_sciences, Manufacturing: manufacturing, Real Estate & Construction: real_estate, Retail & Wholesale: retail_wholesale, Technology: technology.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The time range of the news articles you are targeting, in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format. For example: time_from=20220410T0130. If time_from is specified but time_to is missing, the API will return articles published between the time_from value and the current time.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The time range of the news articles you are targeting, in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sort\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"By default, sort=LATEST and the API will return the latest articles first. You can also set sort=EARLIEST or sort=RELEVANCE based on your use case.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"LATEST\",\n            \"EARLIEST\",\n            \"RELEVANCE\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"By default, limit=50 and the API will return up to 50 matching results. You can also set limit=1000 to output up to 1000 results.\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"function\": \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 883.34,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.946\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"alternative_crypto_fear_greed_index.fear_greed_index.retrieve.v1.fb14b8ee\",\n      \"name\": \"Retrieve Crypto Fear & Greed Index\",\n      \"description\": \"Fetch the current or historical Crypto Fear & Greed Index values from Alternative.me.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Limit the number of returned results. Default is '1'. Use '0' for all available data. The field 'time_until_update' is only returned when limit=1.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"format\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Response format: 'json' (default) or 'csv'.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"json\",\n            \"csv\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"date_format\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Date format for timestamps: 'us' (MM/DD/YYYY), 'cn' or 'kr' (YYYY/MM/DD), 'world' (DD/MM/YYYY). Default is Unix timestamp unless format=csv, in which case default is 'world'.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"us\",\n            \"cn\",\n            \"kr\",\n            \"world\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"Provides a sentiment index for the Bitcoin and crypto market ranging from 0 (Extreme Fear) to 100 (Extreme Greed).\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1187.9,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.999\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"finnhub.stock.insidersentiment.retrieve.v1.dff02940\",\n      \"name\": \"Insider Sentiment\",\n      \"description\": \"Get insider sentiment data for US companies calculated using method discussed <a href=\\\"https://medium.com/@stock-api/finnhub-insiders-sentiment-analysis-cc43f9f64b3a\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">here</a>. The MSPR ranges from -100 for the most negative to 100 for the most positive which can signal price changes in the coming 30-90 days.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbol\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Symbol of the company: AAPL.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"From date: 2020-03-15.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"To date: 2020-03-16.\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"to\": \"2020-03-16\",\n          \"from\": \"2020-03-15\",\n          \"symbol\": \"AAPL\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Finnhub - Free APIs for realtime stock, forex, and cryptocurrency. Company fundamentals, Economic data, and Alternative data.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 3.579,\n        \"success_rate\": 1\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"finnhub.stock.insidersentiment.retrieve.v1.73d5f376\",\n      \"name\": \"Insider Sentiment\",\n      \"description\": \"Get insider sentiment data for US companies calculated using method discussed <a href=\\\"https://medium.com/@stock-api/finnhub-insiders-sentiment-analysis-cc43f9f64b3a\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">here</a>. The MSPR ranges from -100 for the most negative to 100 for the most positive which can signal price changes in the coming 30-90 days.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbol\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Symbol of the company: AAPL.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"From date: 2020-03-15.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"To date: 2020-03-16.\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"to\": \"2020-03-16\",\n          \"from\": \"2020-03-15\",\n          \"symbol\": \"AAPL\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Finnhub - Free APIs for realtime stock, forex, and cryptocurrency. Company fundamentals, Economic data, and Alternative data.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 2.553,\n        \"success_rate\": 1\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"finnhub.stock.insidersentiment.retrieve.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"Insider Sentiment\",\n      \"description\": \"Get insider sentiment data for US companies calculated using method discussed <a href=\\\"https://medium.com/@stock-api/finnhub-insiders-sentiment-analysis-cc43f9f64b3a\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">here</a>. The MSPR ranges from -100 for the most negative to 100 for the most positive which can signal price changes in the coming 30-90 days.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbol\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Symbol of the company: AAPL.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"From date: 2020-03-15.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"To date: 2020-03-16.\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"to\": \"2020-03-16\",\n          \"from\": \"2020-03-15\",\n          \"symbol\": \"AAPL\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Finnhub - Free APIs for realtime stock, forex, and cryptocurrency. Company fundamentals, Economic data, and Alternative data.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 0,\n        \"success_rate\": 0\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"gdelt-data.doc.search.v2.d6d86491\",\n      \"name\": \"GDELT DOC Search API\",\n      \"description\": \"Search GDELT's full-text news and image database across 65 languages with support for advanced query operators and multiple output modes including timelines, galleries, and article lists.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"query\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Search query string (supports boolean operators and field-specific searches).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"mode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Output mode: artlist (article list), timelinevol (volume over time), timelinetone (tone over time), etc.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"ArtList\",\n            \"ArtGallery\",\n            \"ImageCollage\",\n            \"ImageCollageInfo\",\n            \"ImageGallery\",\n            \"ImageCollageShare\",\n            \"TimelineVol\",\n            \"TimelineVolRaw\",\n            \"TimelineVolInfo\",\n            \"TimelineTone\",\n            \"TimelineLang\",\n            \"TimelineSourceCountry\",\n            \"ToneChart\",\n            \"WordCloudImageTags\",\n            \"WordCloudImageWebTags\",\n            \"Timeline\",\n            \"WordCloudEnglish\",\n            \"artlist\",\n            \"timelinevol\",\n            \"timelinetone\",\n            \"timelinelang\",\n            \"timelinegeo\",\n            \"gexf\",\n            \"html\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"format\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Response format. Default is json for most modes.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"html\",\n            \"json\",\n            \"jsonp\",\n            \"csv\",\n            \"rss\",\n            \"HTML\",\n            \"CSV\",\n            \"RSS\",\n            \"RSSArchive\",\n            \"JSON\",\n            \"JSONP\",\n            \"JSONFeed\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"callback\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Callback function name for JSONP output\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"timespan\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Time range to search backwards from now (e.g., '1d', '2w', '3m'). Minimum 15 minutes.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"startdatetime\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Start date/time in YYYYMMDDHHMMSS format.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"enddatetime\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"End date/time in YYYYMMDDHHMMSS format.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"maxrecords\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Maximum number of records to return (up to 250, only applies to ArticleList and ImageCollage modes)\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"timelinesmooth\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Moving window smoothing steps (up to 30) for timeline modes\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"trans\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Enable machine translation widget (only in ArticleList + HTML)\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"googtrans\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sort\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Sorting method for article results. HybridRel is default for post-2018 content.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"DateDesc\",\n            \"DateAsc\",\n            \"ToneDesc\",\n            \"ToneAsc\",\n            \"HybridRel\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"timezoom\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Enable interactive zooming in HTML timeline visualizations.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"yes\",\n            \"no\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"mode\": \"ArtList\",\n          \"query\": \"climate change\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"The Global Database of Events, Language, and Tone (GDELT) monitors the world's broadcast, print, and web news from nearly every corner of every country in over 100 languages and identifies the people, locations, organizations, counts, themes, sources, emotions, quotes, images and events driving our global society every second of every day. GDELT 2.0 updates every 15 minutes with new features including realtime translation of 65 languages and measurement of over 2,300 emotions and themes.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 5785.23,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.024\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"search_id\": \"9252af45-1e2e-4b19-afcd-50445cdd781d\",\n  \"elapsed_time_ms\": 203.7\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":5196,"aggregated":"{\n  \"query\": \"news sentiment relevance score\",\n  \"total\": 10,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"eodhd.sentiments.retrieve.v1.c2c27d35\",\n      \"name\": \"Retrieve Sentiment Data\",\n      \"description\": \"Get sentiment scores for one or more financial instruments (stocks, ETFs, crypto) calculated from news and social media, normalized on a scale from -1 (very negative) to 1 (very positive).\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"s\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"One or more comma-separated tickers, for example: AAPL.US,BTC-USD.CC\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Start date for filtering sentiment data (YYYY-MM-DD)\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"End date for filtering sentiment data (YYYY-MM-DD)\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"s\": \"AAPL.US,BTC-USD.CC\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Access historical end-of-day stock prices, intraday data, US stock options, and real-time prices with free and advanced plans. EODHD provides financial data for 150,000+ tickers, including stocks, ETFs, funds, and currencies worldwide.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1278.53,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.999\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"alphavantage.news_sentiment.query.v1.7aca3c4a\",\n      \"name\": \"Market News & Sentiment\",\n      \"description\": \"Returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from global news outlets covering stocks, crypto, forex, and economic topics.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"function\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The function to call. In this case, NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"tickers\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of stock/crypto/forex symbols to filter articles by (e.g., AAPL,CRYPTO:BTC).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"topics\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of topics to filter by.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"blockchain\",\n            \"earnings\",\n            \"ipo\",\n            \"mergers_and_acquisitions\",\n            \"financial_markets\",\n            \"economy_fiscal\",\n            \"economy_monetary\",\n            \"economy_macro\",\n            \"energy_transportation\",\n            \"finance\",\n            \"life_sciences\",\n            \"manufacturing\",\n            \"real_estate\",\n            \"retail_wholesale\",\n            \"technology\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Start time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format (e.g., 20220410T0130).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"End time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sort\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Sorting method for results.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"LATEST\",\n            \"EARLIEST\",\n            \"RELEVANCE\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Maximum number of results (up to 1000).\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"function\": \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 520.43,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.987\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"gdelt-data.doc.tonechart.retrieve.v2.a7b24341\",\n      \"name\": \"Retrieve Tone Chart\",\n      \"description\": \"Generates a histogram showing the distribution of article tones (from extremely negative to extremely positive) for articles mentioning a specific query over the last 3 months.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"query\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Search query phrase\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"mode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"API operation mode\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"tonechart\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"mode\": \"tonechart\",\n          \"query\": \"climate change\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"The Global Database of Events, Language, and Tone (GDELT) monitors the world's broadcast, print, and web news from nearly every corner of every country in over 100 languages and identifies the people, locations, organizations, counts, themes, sources, emotions, quotes, images and events driving our global society every second of every day. GDELT 2.0 updates every 15 minutes with new features including realtime translation of 65 languages and measurement of over 2,300 emotions and themes.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 19242.44,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.077\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"alphavantage.news_sentiment.retrieve.v1.7aca3c4a\",\n      \"name\": \"Retrieve Market News & Sentiment\",\n      \"description\": \"Returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from premier news outlets around the world, covering stocks, cryptocurrencies, forex, and various financial topics.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"function\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The function name.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"tickers\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of stock/crypto/forex symbols (e.g., COIN,CRYPTO:BTC,FOREX:USD). Filters articles that mention all listed tickers.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"topics\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of topics. Articles must cover all listed topics.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"blockchain\",\n            \"earnings\",\n            \"ipo\",\n            \"mergers_and_acquisitions\",\n            \"financial_markets\",\n            \"economy_fiscal\",\n            \"economy_monetary\",\n            \"economy_macro\",\n            \"energy_transportation\",\n            \"finance\",\n            \"life_sciences\",\n            \"manufacturing\",\n            \"real_estate\",\n            \"retail_wholesale\",\n            \"technology\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Start time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format (e.g., 20220410T0130).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"End time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sort\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Sorting method.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"LATEST\",\n            \"EARLIEST\",\n            \"RELEVANCE\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Maximum number of results (up to 1000).\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"function\": \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 660.49,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.973\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"alphavantage.news_sentiment.query.v1.467a92c0\",\n      \"name\": \"Market News & Sentiment Trending\",\n      \"description\": \"This API returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from a large & growing selection of premier news outlets around the world, covering stocks, cryptocurrencies, forex, and a wide range of topics such as fiscal policy, mergers & acquisitions, IPOs, etc.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"function\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The function of your choice. In this case, function=NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"tickers\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The stock/crypto/forex symbols of your choice. For example: tickers=IBM will filter for articles that mention the IBM ticker; tickers=COIN,CRYPTO:BTC,FOREX:USD will filter for articles that simultaneously mention Coinbase (COIN), Bitcoin (CRYPTO:BTC), and US Dollar (FOREX:USD) in their content.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"topics\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The news topics of your choice. For example: topics=technology will filter for articles that write about the technology sector; topics=technology,ipo will filter for articles that simultaneously cover technology and IPO in their content. Below is the full list of supported topics: Blockchain: blockchain, Earnings: earnings, IPO: ipo, Mergers & Acquisitions: mergers_and_acquisitions, Financial Markets: financial_markets, Economy - Fiscal Policy (e.g., tax reform, government spending): economy_fiscal, Economy - Monetary Policy (e.g., interest rates, inflation): economy_monetary, Economy - Macro/Overall: economy_macro, Energy & Transportation: energy_transportation, Finance: finance, Life Sciences: life_sciences, Manufacturing: manufacturing, Real Estate & Construction: real_estate, Retail & Wholesale: retail_wholesale, Technology: technology.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The time range of the news articles you are targeting, in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format. For example: time_from=20220410T0130. If time_from is specified but time_to is missing, the API will return articles published between the time_from value and the current time.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The time range of the news articles you are targeting, in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sort\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"By default, sort=LATEST and the API will return the latest articles first. You can also set sort=EARLIEST or sort=RELEVANCE based on your use case.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"LATEST\",\n            \"EARLIEST\",\n            \"RELEVANCE\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"By default, limit=50 and the API will return up to 50 matching results. You can also set limit=1000 to output up to 1000 results.\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"function\": \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 883.34,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.946\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"alternative_crypto_fear_greed_index.fear_greed_index.retrieve.v1.fb14b8ee\",\n      \"name\": \"Retrieve Crypto Fear & Greed Index\",\n      \"description\": \"Fetch the current or historical Crypto Fear & Greed Index values from Alternative.me.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Limit the number of returned results. Default is '1'. Use '0' for all available data. The field 'time_until_update' is only returned when limit=1.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"format\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Response format: 'json' (default) or 'csv'.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"json\",\n            \"csv\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"date_format\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Date format for timestamps: 'us' (MM/DD/YYYY), 'cn' or 'kr' (YYYY/MM/DD), 'world' (DD/MM/YYYY). Default is Unix timestamp unless format=csv, in which case default is 'world'.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"us\",\n            \"cn\",\n            \"kr\",\n            \"world\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"Provides a sentiment index for the Bitcoin and crypto market ranging from 0 (Extreme Fear) to 100 (Extreme Greed).\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1187.9,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.999\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"finnhub.stock.insidersentiment.retrieve.v1.dff02940\",\n      \"name\": \"Insider Sentiment\",\n      \"description\": \"Get insider sentiment data for US companies calculated using method discussed <a href=\\\"https://medium.com/@stock-api/finnhub-insiders-sentiment-analysis-cc43f9f64b3a\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">here</a>. The MSPR ranges from -100 for the most negative to 100 for the most positive which can signal price changes in the coming 30-90 days.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbol\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Symbol of the company: AAPL.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"From date: 2020-03-15.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"To date: 2020-03-16.\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"to\": \"2020-03-16\",\n          \"from\": \"2020-03-15\",\n          \"symbol\": \"AAPL\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Finnhub - Free APIs for realtime stock, forex, and cryptocurrency. Company fundamentals, Economic data, and Alternative data.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 3.579,\n        \"success_rate\": 1\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"finnhub.stock.insidersentiment.retrieve.v1.73d5f376\",\n      \"name\": \"Insider Sentiment\",\n      \"description\": \"Get insider sentiment data for US companies calculated using method discussed <a href=\\\"https://medium.com/@stock-api/finnhub-insiders-sentiment-analysis-cc43f9f64b3a\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">here</a>. The MSPR ranges from -100 for the